{
  "stem": "4693.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And after short while, they offered me a job, a uniformed job, under contract.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I started as a supply officer, I finished as a legal adviser, with the same right and privileges as a full colonel in American army.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I had a very good life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was-- you had parties with the military government, officers-- I mean, they were-- I had a beautiful home with a swimming pool in the forest, you know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And private car and chauffeur, duty car and driver.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "A very great life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Germany?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Assisting in the courts where displaced person were involved or where it was some-- German stories, as a friend of court.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Taking care about different problem-- Jewish problem, problems of the inmates of the-- former inmates of the camps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was pretty busy with this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Plenty-- the American style conferences all around Germany, you know, going from one place to another, driving hundreds of kilometers for two hours' meeting.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Going back, you never knew why you came, you knew never knew why you came back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I made plenty of friends in UNRRA, which were later became IRO, International Refuge Organization.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] But the problem was this was a fool's paradise.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody was telling me that I should go to the United States.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was the dream of everybody in Europe, how to go to United States.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was in a special privilege position because I was born in Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The quotas to United States for immigration were not according to your nationality, or citizenship, but according to place of birth.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were established in the beginning of the century, according to the percentage of migrants then already being in United States.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Germans had a quota of 26,000.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
